snippet.title: Skystrider | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Music credit - Scott Buckley https://www.scottbuckley.com.au/
Voice credit - Francesca Mintowt-Czyz

Skystrider is a 3D third-person action platformer game set in a ruined world. Traverse paths through clouds and tides towards a new future. 

Developed by Ichor Games LLC
